  "title": "Process Technician (Permanent Night Shift – 12 Hours | 7PM – 7AM)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Work Location : 6 Tampines Industrial Avenue 5 </strong><br /><strong>Work Hours : Work 4 days, Off 3 days; Work 3 days, Off 4 days</strong><br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities</strong> <br />• Assist engineer to work on all process related functions to ensure an efficiency production <br />• Assist in creating a proper process operation flow as per customer & business requirement <br />• Ensure production work instruction is properly maintained include SFC control process & SAP maintain process <br />• Participate in Kaizen activities <br />• Provide trainings over work instruction to production. <br />• To support on the NPI Process and production on mass run <br />• Participate in ISO activities (implementation & maintain)<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong><br />• Nitec & above qualification in engineering with at least 1-3 years of working experience in process. <br />• Good team player <br />• Ability to work with Peers, engineers, and superiors <br />• Able to multi-task & work under pressure Compliance with RBA standards</p>",
